data.description: Are you looking for an amazing home to entertain in? Are you looking to be close to Trilith Studios? Are you looking for that finished walk out basement? Your look is over! Traditional home on full basement with a bedroom, media area and full bath with its own outside entrance to the back yard! Love the main living area! Tons of natural light beams through multiple windows on the front and back of the house. Huge family room open to the large eat in kitchen and extends from the front to the back of the house. Enjoy movie night in front of the warm fireplace. Large deck off the kitchen is great for grilling. Large owner's suite with your "Calgon take me away tub" with large double vanities with plenty of storage. Great neighborhood if you want to be active! Swimming, tennis, and a great place to go for a run. Less than a mile from the front door to Bennetts Middle School. This home is 5 miles to Fayette Center and 4.5 miles to Publix in Peachtree City and just 7 miles to Lake Peachtree. Its 4 miles to the studios. Opportunity to assume the seller's loan at an amazing rate!
